    <div class="hf-card"><div class="hf-icon hf-eth">Ξ</div><div class="hf-info"><div class="hf-name">Ethereum</div><div class="hf-price">$3,521</div></div><div class="hf-chg hf-up">+1.87%</div></div>
    <div class="hf-card"><div class="hf-icon hf-sol">◎</div><div class="hf-info"><div class="hf-name">Solana</div><div class="hf-price">$142.80</div></div><div class="hf-chg hf-up">+3.65%</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="section about-sec" id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-img-wrap reveal-l">
      <div class="about-photo">💼</div>
      <div class="about-badge-box"><div class="about-badge-val">15+</div><div class="about-badge-lbl">Years Experience</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal-r">
      <div class="s-eyebrow">About Tabuwul FX</div>
      <h2 class="s-title">Connect with the <span class="hl">Right Broker</span></h2>
      <p class="about-body">Whether you are experienced or a beginner, connecting with the right broker is everything. Tabuwul FX is a leading trade and investment company in the UK with years of industry experience. We specialize in Cryptocurrency, Forex, and Stock market investments.</p>
      <div class="about-checks">
        <div class="check-item"><div class="check-icon">✓</div>High Frequency Trading</div>
        <div class="check-item"><div class="check-icon">✓</div>Instant Withdrawals</div>
        <div class="check-item"><div class="check-icon">✓</div>Guaranteed ROIs</div>
        <div class="check-item"><div class="check-icon">✓</div>Multiple Funding Options</div>
        <div class="check-item"><div class="check-icon">✓</div>Fast and Secure</div>
        <div class="check-item"><div class="check-icon">✓</div>Learn from Customer Feedback</div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-primary" onclick="openModal('signup')">Read More →</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="section hiw-sec">
  <div class="s-eyebrow s-center reveal">How It Work</div>
  <h2 class="s-title s-center reveal">Three Simple Steps To Start <span class="hl">Earning</span></h2>
  <div class="s-divider reveal"></div>
  <div class="hiw-steps">
    <div class="hiw-step reveal">
      <div class="step-circle">01</div>
      <div class="step-title">Create Account</div>
      <p class="step-desc">Create your account and get started with your investment journey. No complicated verification required.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hiw-step reveal">
      <div class="step-circle">02</div>
      <div class="step-title">Make Deposit</div>
      <p class="step-desc">After account creation, simply make deposits from the funding page in your dashboard using any payment method.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hiw-step reveal">
      <div class="step-circle">03</div>
      <div class="step-title">Earn &amp; Get Paid</div>
      <p class="step-desc">You can make withdrawals as soon as you start making profits. Funds are sent directly to your account instantly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT WE DO -->
<section class="section wwd-sec">
  <div class="s-eyebrow s-center reveal">What We Do</div>
  <h2 class="s-title s-center reveal">We Create Solutions for Your <span class="hl">Investment Needs</span></h2>
  <div class="s-divider reveal"></div>
  <div class="wwd-grid">
    <div class="wwd-card reveal"><span class="wwd-icon">👥</span><div class="wwd-title">Business Finance Strategy</div><p class="wwd-desc">Devise and implement business strategies that drive success for an entire business or division, technology, or asset.</p></div>
    <div class="wwd-card reveal"><span class="wwd-icon">📋</span><div class="wwd-title">Portfolio &amp; Resource Allocation</div><p class="wwd-desc">By balancing and optimizing the many competing assets and initiatives, we achieve deep and lasting improvements.</p></div>
    <div class="wwd-card reveal"><span class="wwd-icon">🏢</span><div class="wwd-title">Organization &amp; Decision Process</div><p class="wwd-desc">Organizations are designed to be effective and efficient. The processes require cross-functional thinking.</p></div>
    <div class="wwd-card reveal"><span class="wwd-icon">📊</span><div class="wwd-title">Decision &amp; Risk Analytic</div><p class="wwd-desc">Our decision risk analytics empower clients to develop rational decision-making models and development strategies.</p></div>
    <div class="wwd-card reveal"><span class="wwd-icon">🏦</span><div class="wwd-title">Banking &amp; Capital Markets</div><p class="wwd-desc">The venues where savings and investments are channeled between the suppliers who have capital and those who need it.</p></div>
    <div class="wwd-card reveal"><span class="wwd-icon">🌐</span><div class="wwd-title">Modern &amp; Tribe Workplace</div><p class="wwd-desc">Redefine your workplace value equation that encourage staff to work more attentively and gracefully.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INVESTMENT PLANS -->
<section class="section plans-sec" id="plans">
  <div class="s-eyebrow s-center reveal">Our Investment Plans</div>
  <h2 class="s-title s-center reveal">Choose Your <span class="hl">Investment Tier</span></h2>
  <div class="s-divider reveal"></div>
  <div class="plans-grid">
    <div class="plan-card reveal">
      <div class="plan-icon-wrap">🌱</div>
