<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section faq-sec" id="faq">
  <div class="s-eyebrow s-center reveal">FAQ</div>
  <h2 class="s-title s-center reveal">Do you have any <span class="hl">Questions?</span></h2>
  <div class="s-divider reveal"></div>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item reveal"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is bitcoin ? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Bitcoin is a decentralized digital currency without a central bank or single administrator. It can be sent from user to user on the peer-to-peer bitcoin network without the need for intermediaries. It was invented in 2008 by the pseudonymous Satoshi Nakamoto.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item reveal"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Who Developed Bitcoin? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Bitcoin was developed by an unknown person or group of people using the name Satoshi Nakamoto. The original Bitcoin whitepaper was published in October 2008. The first Bitcoin software was released in January 2009.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item reveal"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is Bitcoin Mining? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Bitcoin mining is the process of creating new bitcoin by solving extremely complicated math problems that verify transactions in the currency. Miners receive Bitcoin as a reward for completing transaction blocks added to the blockchain.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item reveal"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is Bitcoin Used For Illegal Activities? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">While Bitcoin has been used for some illegal activities, it is primarily used for legitimate purposes. The transparent nature of the blockchain actually makes it easier to track criminal activity compared to cash. The vast majority of Bitcoin transactions are for legal commerce and investment.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item reveal"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How do I start investing with Tabuwul FX? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Simply create a free account, choose your investment plan, and make your first deposit. Our team will guide you through the process. Minimum investment starts from $1,000 for our Starter Tier plan.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item reveal"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How fast are withdrawals processed? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Tabuwul FX processes withdrawals instantly. Once you request a withdrawal, funds are sent directly to your wallet or bank account within 24 hours. We support bank transfers, crypto withdrawals, and multiple payment options.</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

